{"tid":755390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[爆屎渠當景點？]中國建造100米高瀑布大樓","createTime":"2018-07-25T07:27:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T16:53:25.000Z","uid":19454,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"c792a3a82df4d4824e9d57a2057868347d3cda3a","tid":755390,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T07:27:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn.gameover.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/25080110/page8810.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.gameover.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F25080110%2Fpage8810.jpg&h=16fe2ec6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國經常都有石破天驚嘅建築物，之前網上都傳唔少，最近傳到去外國有呢楝人造瀑布大樓。位於貴陽市嘅觀山湖，100米高，想睇瀑布？唔駛去到郊區，喺市區就睇到，係咪威先。不過電費好貴，開放一個鐘已經要用800蚊以上嘅人仔。有網民話睇落似漏水，有人話嘥電唔環保，亦有人話唔駛擔心，因為中國製造應該唔會用到好耐。不過都有支持者嘅，佢哋話可以改善空氣污染，又可以宣傳附近知名嘅黃果樹瀑布，好正面呀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://gameover.com.hk/?p=411135\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgameover.com.hk%2F%3Fp%3D411135&d=FWxduykNtOOU8L%2FspW3vaC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=1a43d23e\" target=\"_blank\">http://gameover.com.hk/?p=411135</a>"},{"pid":"1e69fc440cb0a09dc9fcb2102e74fc7df0960a63","tid":755390,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T07:27:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn.gameover.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/25074835/bu3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.gameover.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F25074835%2Fbu3.jpg&h=9e8bf30e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3822b51c8576d27f2c58ebb132fd7c718723cf94","tid":755390,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T07:28:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn.gameover.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/25074841/bu6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.gameover.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F25074841%2Fbu6.jpg&h=a81ec04d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"373596657e6c1662e9c556c17a0e0121c32dcc29","tid":755390